<h1>DAISY Book Upload </h1>
<p>
To add image descriptions to a DAISY book in the Poet library, follow these steps:
</p>
<ol>
<li>Click the Browse button (below) and choose a DAISY book (zip) file from your local drive to upload.</li>
<li>If the book is password protected, enter your password in the field.</li>
<li>Click the Upload button.</li>
</ol>
<p>
After the upload process completes, you will see the book contents in the right frame and the image navigation bar in the left frame.
</p>
<p>
Enter or edit descriptions by typing text in the edit area under each image and clicking the Submit button to save each one. When finished with your session, close the browser.
</p>

<%= form_tag("/upload_book/submit", {:multipart => true}) do %>
<p><label for="upload_file">Select Daisy book file</label> : 
<%= file_field_tag 'book' %> </p>
<p><label for="upload_file">Enter password (if needed)</label> :
<%= password_field_tag 'password' %> </p>
<%= submit_tag "Upload" %>
<% end %>

